title: About | Positively Records
text: The Story of the StoreLaunched in 1984, Positively Records, is a Record Store run for music lovers, by music lovers. Our aim is to offer music fans an easy and simple way to discover great new music on both independent and major labels.What started out as a passionate hobby for music collector Kevin Sandrdige, exploded into every music lover's haven. Many of the selections in the store are records that Kevin also owns at home. We not only sell vinyls and CDs from artists all over the world, but pride ourselves on supporting local and upcoming talents. If there’s anything in particular you are looking for, feel free to drop us a line and we’ll be happy to help.Get in Touch
